                        ↓
              POWDER STORAGE & BLENDING
                        ↓
              ADDITIVE MANUFACTURING
         (LPBF for Al, EB-PBF for Ti-HEA)
                        ↓
              POST-PROCESSING
         (stress relief, HIP, surface finish)
                        ↓
